summary: This test module validates the RetinaNet detection model provided by MONAI. It checks that the model produces correctly shaped outputs for various ResNet backbones, can be exported to ONNX, and is compatible with TorchScript scripting, using parameterized test cases and version-dependent skips.
business_intent: Guarantee the reliability and deployability of the RetinaNet model for medical imaging detection pipelines, ensuring it works across different backbone architectures and can be exported for production environments.
